name: QSTAR
description: The purpose of Q* is to track the progress and news of OpenAIs generative new product called the same name “Q Star”. This is an AGI that is currently in development at OpenAI under the leadership of Sam Altman. Our mission is to educate the crypto world of developments and soon use the OpenAI API to allow testing of newer versions of ChatGPT and hopefully in the not so far future, Q Star itself.
